        p_{\kappa}p_{\tau}\,\,\,
    e^{-\frac{1}{2}p\cdot R\cdot p}
    &=&
     (2\pi)^{D/2}
     R^{-1}_{{\kappa}{\tau}}
    (\det R)^{-1/2}.
 \end{eqnarray}
\end{small}
Renaming a dummy index $\kappa\to\lambda$:
